Frederick Peters (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frederick_Peters_(actor) 0 Frederick Peters (June 30, 1884 – April 23, 1963), was an American film actor. He appeared in 17 films between years 1918 and 1936. He was born in Waltham, Massachusetts and died in Hollywood, California.
